N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 606.71 - Exemptions from fees or charges

State Regulations

The board reserves the right to exempt from the
provisions of these sections, as to the payment of charges or fees, religious, charitable or fraternal organizations or associations, or similar organizations
or associations; provided, however, in case of any such exemption, all the
other rules and regulations herein shall be fully complied
with. Notes
